// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3535 — Mass File Rename (safepay)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 7611eb50-1479-5def-b552-90599f63c394

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
